107
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,440
No, Mr. Lu.

108
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,130
It's not your fault.

109
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,800
It's me,

110
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,090
I just can't do anything right.

111
