117
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,360
For the mobile game promotion this time,

118
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,280
Meiduo will provide us with

119
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:41,610
the best resources and platform support.

120
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,000
But correspondingly,

121
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,640
