122
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,720
the client has also set

123
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,450
very, very high expectations.

124
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:48,920
So I am asking all of you,

125
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,280
the bloggers sitting here.

126
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,080
You must maximize

127
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:54,159
