128
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:54,840
We'll

129
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,040
create a promotional matrix

130
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,840
and boost the traffic together.

131
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,250
Okay.

132
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,159
Got it, Aiwei.

133
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,360
Well...

134
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:02,720
Compile all the proposals

135
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,760
and give them to me later.

136
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,560
Produce the drafts first.

137
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,160
We'll go over them a few more times later.

138
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,720
Ensure both quantity and quality.

139
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,180
Understood. Don't worry.

140
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,000
Alright then.

141
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,600
Have a good discussion then.

142
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,800
Okay.

143
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:28,000
Don't hit me.

144
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,039
What do I do?

145
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,880
Where do I go?

146
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,730
