147
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,240
This is so hard.

148
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,600
Babe.

149
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,250
I'm home.

150
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,240
You're back.

151
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:52,840
Come here.

152
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:53,880
Hurry up.

153
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:55,480
Quick.

154
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,160
What's wrong?

155
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:56,960
Let me ask you.

156
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,360
Do you know how to play games?

157
00:08:59,360 --> 00:08:59,890
Yes, I do.

158
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,800
I used to play.

159
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,560
But not anymore.

160
