I'm too busy with work and it takes up time.

161
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,340
Did you use to play 'Zhu Xian'?

162
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:06,960
'Zhu Xian'?

163
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,360
I actually did play it.

164
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,400
Back in high school,

165
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,860
