166
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,520
But it was a single-player version then.

167
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,840
I still remember I was the first one on my dorm floor

168
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,770
to beat the game.

169
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,760
All the guys rushed to my room

170
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,160
to see the ending screen.

171
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,200
You're amazing.

172
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:24,700
How should I put it?

173
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,240
Maybe for a guy,

174
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,900
youth isn't complete without games.

175
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,410
That's true.

176
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,380
Have you eaten?

177
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,720
Not yet.

178
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,040
I'll go cook then.

179
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,080
Games.

180
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,280
Games,

181
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,760
