182
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,200
But people

183
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,120
are real.

184
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:16,280
So I can start from the emotions

185
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,160
of the gamers,

186
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,360
and look for

187
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,960
stories of ordinary people.

188
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,640
Just looking.

189
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,200
Hello.

190
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,720
What are you looking for?

191
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,970
Excuse me, is your boss Wang Dong here?

192
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:01,640
Boss.

193
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:04,360
Someone is here to see you again.

194
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:05,480
Thank you.

195
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:06,340
No problem.

196
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:09,880
Hello.

197
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,560
My name is Jiangzi.

198
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:13,280
I am a short video creator.

199
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,000
I got a task at work

200
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,600
to shoot a promotional video for Jade Dynasty.

201
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,080
I saw on Tieba

202
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:21,840
that the story of you and your fiancée is very touching.

203
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,840
I was wondering if we could

204
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,480
turn your story into a video.

205
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:30,080
I posted this thread

206
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:33,260
just to commemorate my personal relationship.

207
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:35,560
I never thought about using it for promotion.

208
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,040
So about what you said about shooting a video...

209
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:38,040
Here's the thing.

210
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,160
I really think

211
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:41,040
your story is very moving

212
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:43,200
and deserves to be seen by everyone.

213
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,680
If you are willing,

214
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,200
the materials I use

215
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,640
will be approved by you.

216
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,400
If it's inconvenient for you to disclose

217
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,320
your real information,

218
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,580
we can use pseudonyms.

219
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,400
Rest assured,

220
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,480
I won't use your story for free.

221
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,360
We can discuss the remuneration.

222
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,490
You misunderstand.

223
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,880
I'm not after fame,

224
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:01,940
nor do I want money.

225
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,210
I can let you shoot my story.

226
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,200
It's just that

227
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:14,940
I have one request.

228
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:20,880
This house...

229
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:25,480
Xiaoran and I lived here together for three years.

230
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,080
After she left,

231
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:36,300
I haven't changed the layout here at all.

232
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,280
It has always remained the same.

233
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,760
This girl is Xiaoran.

234
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:49,010
She's so beautiful.

235
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,720
How did you meet?

236
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,340
Speaking of which,

237
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,360
it's quite funny.

238
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,940
Five years ago,

239
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:07,080
I was working as a clerk in an internet cafe.

240
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,770
When I had nothing to do,

241
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,160
I often played games.

242
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:11,440
Once I met a noob.

243
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:12,960
She was so bad

244
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,800
and kept dragging me down.

245
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:15,930
I couldn't stand it,

246
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:18,380
so I started arguing with her in the game.

247
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,800
But the argument just got worse.

248
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,720
Then,

249
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,720
just arguing wasn't enough.

250
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,720
So we arranged an offline fight.

251
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,160
A fight?

252
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,280
You didn't go up, Yilu Weikuang?

253
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:40,680
I have something to do.

254
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:41,360
You guys go first.

255
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,120
We'll go up first then.

256
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,450
Okay.

257
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:12,040
Didn't you say you were going to beat me down?

258
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,040
Why don't you even dare to look at me?

259
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,240
You are.

260
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,520
Sanwan Zhangfei.

261
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,600
I never used to believe

262
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,860
in love at first sight.

263
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,560
But the moment I saw Xiaoran,

264
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,440
I knew

265
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:35,320
