266
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:45,760
That was truly the happiest

267
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:47,240
time of my life.

268
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:50,210
Xiaoran is a Beijing local.

269
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,410
She comes from a good family

270
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:54,960
and is a graduate student from a top university.

271
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,490
As for me,

272
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,820
I was just a penniless shop clerk.

273
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,800
Thank you.

274
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:04,770
Is it pretty?

275
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:06,280
It is pretty.

276
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:07,640
But it's just a 20-yuan item.

277
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:09,040
Do you really like it that much?

278
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:10,300
Who said it was 20 yuan?

279
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,810
This is a genuine huge diamond.

280
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:17,250
Xiaoran.

281
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:20,440
When I make money in the future,

282
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:22,440
I will definitely buy you a real one.

283
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,580
Her friends and family

284
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:32,880
didn't approve of us.

285
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:36,290
But Xiaoran didn't care what others said,

286
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,440
and without hesitation

287
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,300
stayed with me.

288
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,480
I was determined,

289
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:42,900
thinking I must earn enough money

290
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:44,570
to give her a stable future.

291
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,010
Then I would propose to her.

292
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:48,520
So I scraped together

293
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:50,520
and opened this electronics store.

294
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:52,960
Xiaoran was about to graduate at the time.

295
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,820
She could have found a stable job,

296
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:57,960
but she came to help me without hesitation.

297
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,280
We couldn't afford to hire anyone,

298
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:02,240
so we did everything from decoration to management

299
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,120
by ourselves.

300
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,250
Then I'll unveil it.

301
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,180
Just when I thought

302
00:16:44,560 --> 00:16:46,200
I could finally fulfill my promise,

303
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:48,060
When we were about to get married,

304
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:50,280
God played a huge joke on me.

305
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:51,920
Xiaoran

306
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:54,290
was diagnosed with cancer.

307
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:43,000
Chemotherapy was very painful.

308
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,840
To distract herself,

309
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:47,690
Xiaoran spent a long time every day

310
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,610
immersing herself in the game.

311
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:51,570
In the later stages,

312
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:53,730
she became emotionally unstable.

313
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,170
When she was in pain,

314
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:57,170
she would lose her temper at me.

315
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,400
I thought to myself then,

316
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:02,620
it's good that she has the energy to be angry.

317
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,610
As long as she could get better,

318
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:07,380
I wouldn't mind her taking it out on me every day.

319
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:09,250
Unfortunately,

320
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:11,000
in the end,

321
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:13,300
I still couldn't save her.

322
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:24,760
When I was sorting through Xiaoran's belongings,

323
00:19:24,760 --> 00:19:25,960
I found her diary.

324
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,250
That was when I realized

325
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:30,580
she secretly created an alt account.

326
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:33,560
Everywhere she went in the game,

327
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:36,660
she farmed various gears and sent them to me.

328
00:19:45,560 --> 00:19:46,240
Wang Dong.

329
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:49,160
By the time you read this diary,

330
00:19:49,760 --> 00:19:51,690
I guess I'm no longer in this world.

331
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,800
Have you seen my alt account?

332
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:57,440
That is the last gift I prepared for you.

333
00:19:58,240 --> 00:20:00,000
I hope you like this gift,

334
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:03,000
and I hope you will always remember me.

335
00:20:04,040 --> 00:20:05,570
If forever is not possible,

336
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:08,730
then let this memory last a little longer,

337
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:10,520
just a little longer.

338
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:13,700
I will always love you.

339
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:18,610
But I only have the account,

340
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,240
not the password.

341
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:24,410
I consulted customer service before,

342
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:25,960
but they said

343
00:20:27,080 --> 00:20:28,280
because Xiaoran and I

344
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:30,360
are not legally married,

345
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,440
so I have no right

346
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:35,240
to inherit this virtual legacy.

347
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,340
This is my biggest regret.

348
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:50,580
I mentioned before

349
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:52,800
that I have a request.

350
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:55,980
I hope you can step up and help me fight for it.

351
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:58,180
I want to get these gears back.

352
00:21:00,600 --> 00:21:02,000
They are all the memories

353
00:21:02,120 --> 00:21:03,250
Xiaoran left for me.

354
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:14,690
Don't worry.

355
00:21:16,520 --> 00:21:18,920
I will definitely do my best to fight for it.

356
00:21:20,760 --> 00:21:22,220
Once they know your story,

357
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:24,480
there will be a solution.

358
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:29,160
Thank you.

359
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:39,600
I will never meet a girl

360
00:21:39,600 --> 00:21:41,330
who treats me so well in my life.

361
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:47,240
If you pass by Qingyun Mountain in the game,

362
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:51,420
please tell her

363
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:56,160
I miss her a lot

364
00:21:59,000 --> 00:21:59,760
and love her.

365
00:22:02,280 --> 00:22:02,960
Now,

366
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:04,480
Wang Dong is still running

367
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:06,010
the shop he and Xiaoran had.

368
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,600
He said

369
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:10,380
although business is bad,

370
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:12,680
he will keep it open.

371
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:21,880
Mr. Yang,

372
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,440
what do you think?

373
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:28,760
What do you think?

374
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,880
Although the video is a bit long,

375
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:31,640
I think

376
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,040
we don't need to cut anything.

377
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:33,570
Perfect.

378
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:37,560
I think life is the best planner.

379
00:22:37,840 --> 00:22:38,370
Jiangzi,

380
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:40,660
you really hit the jackpot this time.

381
00:22:43,040 --> 00:22:45,370
Audience feedback is the most authentic.

382
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,400
This story

383
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:47,640
has tear-jerking

384
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:48,720
and painful moments.

385
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:50,580
The emotional part is just right,

386
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:53,100
and there's no excessive marketing.

387
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,860
I think it's very good.

388
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:27,420
What are you doing?

389
00:23:31,120 --> 00:23:31,880
I'm at home.

390
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,440
What's up, Mr. Lu?

391
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:53,040
Nothing.

392
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:55,100
Are you free recently?

393
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:57,040
Let's have a meal together some day.

394
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,240
And we can also discuss

395
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,960
how to be a good influencer.

396
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:04,200
Sure.

397
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,120
I'm available anytime.

398
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:07,840
It depends on your schedule.

399
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:08,520
My treat.

400
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:25,980
Then let's do it on New Year's Eve.

401
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,860
After all, it's a special day,

402
00:24:28,120 --> 00:24:30,450
and I should eat with someone I want to see.

403
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,880
It's quite hot today.

404
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:07,850
The water dispenser in the office is also broken.

405
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,640
I haven't had a sip of water all day.

406
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:10,770
I'm dying of thirst.

407
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:14,320
Who drank from this cup?

408
00:25:14,320 --> 00:25:15,040
Is it clean?

409
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:36,820
Have you eaten?

410
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,620
If not, I can order something.

411
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,540
I'm not hungry.

412
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:45,530
Order for yourself if you want.

413
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:48,800
I'm not hungry either.

414
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:50,260
I was just afraid you were.

415
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,250
Where is the remote?

416
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:05,320
I left it on the coffee table before work.

417
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:07,800
You are just like this,

418
00:26:07,800 --> 00:26:09,800
always putting things everywhere.

419
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,480
I can never find them.

420
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:12,120
Really,

421
00:26:12,120 --> 00:26:13,920
when will you change this bad habit?

422
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:15,040
You always

423
00:26:15,040 --> 00:26:15,680
It's not here.

424
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:16,440
hide things here and there.

425
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:17,840
Are you sitting on it?

426
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:19,400
It's not here.

427
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,240
What are you doing?

428
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,000
Why did you hit my back?

429
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,080
Are you supposed to hit my back?

430
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,040
So what if I hit you?

431
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:24,160
Let me tell you, if you hit me again, I'll...

432
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:24,890
You'll what?

433
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:27,200
I'm sorry.

434
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:30,640
Honey.

435
00:26:31,840 --> 00:26:32,920
I know we've been

436
00:26:33,040 --> 00:26:34,600
having some issues recently.

437
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:35,480
I also remember

438
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:37,200
what I said when I proposed to you.

439
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:38,240
I said I would spoil you,

440
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:40,900
love you, and protect you for the rest of my life.

441
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:42,680
I haven't done a good job.

442
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:46,240
I've learned from my mistakes.

443
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:46,800
Really,

444
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:48,540
I've reflected on myself.

445
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:50,850
I've been watching you lately.

446
00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:52,520
You are so persistent,

447
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:53,450
serious,

448
00:26:53,760 --> 00:26:54,840
and hardworking about your job.

449
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:55,570
I've decided

450
00:26:56,120 --> 00:26:57,640
that I won't criticize you anymore.

451
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:58,440
I support you.

452
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,720
So honey,

453
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:03,810
please stop being mad at me.

454
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:15,560
Really?

455
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:22,720
Honey.

456
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:24,160
A while ago,

457
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:26,960
didn't you say you wanted to go to Gubei Water Town?

458
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:29,080
I recently heard from my colleagues

459
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:32,120
that spending New Year's Eve at Gubei Water Town is really fun.

460
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:33,760
There are beautiful fireworks shows

461
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:35,090
and a masquerade party.

462
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:36,480
I also know a

463
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:38,540
very delicious popular restaurant.

464
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:41,800
Let's go spend New Year's Eve together.

465
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:43,880
I asked you before,

466
00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:46,040
didn't you say you didn't want to go?

467
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:48,080
It doesn't matter if I don't want to go.

468
00:27:48,080 --> 00:27:50,010
What matters is that you want to go.

469
00:27:51,080 --> 00:27:51,720
Really?

470
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,520
Okay then.

471
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:56,570
You promised me,

472
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:58,080
no going back.

473
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,000
Then I'll go online right now

474
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:03,050
and make the reservations.

475
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:37,760
Mr. Lu,

476
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:38,720
I'm sorry.

477
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:41,000
I have other plans for New Year's Eve.

478
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,920
Let's talk about it later.

479
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:47,840
Okay.

480
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:49,650
Have a good time in advance.

481
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:10,370
Come,

482
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:11,530
please come inside.

483
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,200
Have a seat anywhere.

484
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:16,130
Although our company is not the largest in scale,

485
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:17,900
we are the first in the country

486
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:20,450
to manufacture intelligent robots as an OEM.

487
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,720
We have three production lines.

488
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:24,720
Now many well-known domestic enterprises...

489
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:25,440
Why did you put it there?

490
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:27,170
All come to us for OEM services.

491
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:31,240
What do you think of this one?

492
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:31,880
This one,

493
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:32,960
I think is

494
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,480
out of all the OEMs we've seen,

495
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:36,340
the most qualified and powerful.

496
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:39,340
I lean toward this one too.

497
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:45,040
How large is your order?

498
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,810
We're ordering 15 medical robots.

499
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:50,200
Only 15?

500
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:56,440
Here's the thing, Director.

501
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:57,800
As they say, strangers the first time, friends the second.

502
00:29:57,800 --> 00:29:58,960
Since it's our first time working together,

503
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:01,000
we definitely need some time to adjust to each other.

504
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,440
If things go well,

505
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:04,520
we'll entrust all our future production

506
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:05,240
to you.

507
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:06,320
Right.

508
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:07,440
So, you see,

509
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,970
could you give us a better price this time?

510
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:12,240
How about this?

511
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,160
For this time,

512
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:14,400
we'll keep the price as is.

513
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,720
If we continue cooperating in the future

514
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:16,680
and everything goes well,

515
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,540
we can negotiate the price again.

516
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:19,840
All right.

517
00:30:19,840 --> 00:30:20,920
Okay.

518
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:22,320
Then it's settled.

519
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:22,840
Okay.

520
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,080
Here, have some water.

521
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:24,720
Thank you.

522
00:31:01,840 --> 00:31:02,720
Who is it?

523
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,040
I don't know.

524
00:31:28,280 --> 00:31:29,480
Let me take this call.

525
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,320
Who is it?

526
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,840
I'm a clerk at Wang Dong's store.

527
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:38,000
We met once before.

528
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:39,090
Do you remember?

529
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:40,120
Yes.

530
00:31:40,120 --> 00:31:40,920
What's wrong?

531
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:44,280
Wang Dong is a total jerk.

532
00:31:44,760 --> 00:31:46,020
You were fooled by him.

533
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,080
He didn't actually want to marry

534
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:50,880
his deceased girlfriend at all.

535
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:05,440
What's wrong?

536
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:07,840
Something came up at work.

537
00:32:07,840 --> 00:32:08,960
I have to go deal with it.

538
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:09,920
I won't watch it.

539
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:10,610
Okay.

540
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:11,850
Hurry up and go then.

541
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:13,160
I'll take you.

542
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:13,880
No need.

543
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:14,720
Just go home and wait for me.

544
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:15,780
I'll be right back.

545
00:32:16,680 --> 00:32:17,940
Let's leave together.

546
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:22,140
Excuse me, please.

547
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:30,400
You mean I was scammed?

548
00:32:31,320 --> 00:32:32,650
What exactly happened?

549
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:34,120
Half a year ago,

550
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:36,000
I started working at Wang Dong's shop.

551
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:38,200
Customers would often come to the shop.

552
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,600
They were all from Tieba,

553
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:40,760
having seen his post,

554
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:42,320
and came specifically to support him.

555
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:43,320
That's how I found out

556
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:44,380
he had such a story.

557
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:45,880
At first,

558
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,620
I thought he was a good man,

559
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:49,680
and I even sympathized with him.

560
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:50,680
Until later,

561
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:51,640
one time,

562
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:54,360
on his computer,

563
00:32:54,360 --> 00:32:55,890
I accidentally found this.

564
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,920
2020.

565
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,480
Back then, Xiao Ran

566
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:10,200
hadn't even passed away yet,

567
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,880
and he was already cheating.

568
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:14,640
His so-called devoted lover persona is all made up.

569
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:16,080
Everything he did

570
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:18,660
was just to attract business to his shop.

571
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,040
Jiangzi.

572
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:37,720
What's the matter?

573
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:39,280
Why the rush?

574
00:33:40,360 --> 00:33:41,000
Ms. Aiwei.

575
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:43,120
The promotional video you shot

576
00:33:43,120 --> 00:33:44,720
is highly rated internally.

577
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,880
Especially the story of the terminally ill girlfriend.

578
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,040
Our boss watched it

579
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:49,370
and was very satisfied.

580
00:33:49,440 --> 00:33:50,520
He has decided to use it

581
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:52,040
as the main promotional video

582
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:53,600
for this mobile game launch.

583
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,600
Thank you so much.

584
